flowchart TD
    A["New Supplier Quality Audit Request"] --> B["Cortex: Audit Planning & Validation"]
    B --> C{Audit Passes Validation?}
    C -->|Yes| D["Cortex: Certification Acceptance"]
    D --> E["UI: Notify Supplier of Acceptance"]
    E --> F["PB: Update Supplier Quality Status"]
    F --> G["End"]
    C -->|No| H["Cortex: Remediation Plan Generation"]
    H --> I["UI: Present Remediation Steps to Supplier"]
    I --> J["PB: Create CAPA Request"]
    J --> K["Cortex: CAPA Closure Monitoring"]
    K --> L{CAPA Closed On Time?}
    L -->|Yes| M["PB: Update CAPA Status"]
    M --> N["UI: Notify Supplier of Closure"]
    N --> G
    L -->|No| O["Cortex: Escalate CAPA"]
    O --> P["UI: Notify Quality Manager"]
    P --> Q["PB: Escalation Log"]
    Q --> R["Cortex: Process Capability Initiative Prioritization"]
    R --> S{Process Capability Improvement Needed?}
    S -->|Yes| T["PB: Allocate Resources for Capability Initiative"]
    T --> U["UI: Track Process Capability Metrics"]
    U --> V["Cortex: NPI Quality Gate Review"]
    V --> W{NPI Quality Ready?}
    W -->|Yes| X["PB: Approve NPI with Supplier"]
    W -->|No| Y["Cortex: Escalate NPI Risk"]
    Y --> Z["UI: Notify Engineering Team"]
    Z --> G
    S -->|No| V